OL,7,FThree men who had been jailed over
OL,8,Fexlosive offences more than 30 years
OL,9,Fago have had their convictions
OL,10,Foverturned by the court of Appeal.
OL,12,FDeclan John Murphy, Declan John Moen
OL,13,Fand Conor Gilmore were jailed in 1991
OL,14,Fover a plot to attack the RUC football
OL,15,Fteam.
