OL,7,FDeclan John Murphy, brother of former
OL,8,FSinn Fein Stormont minister Conor
OL,9,FMurphy who served nine years in prison
OL,10,Fsaid the overturning of his conviction
OL,11,Fis a "personal vindication".
OL,13,FHe added it was also a "damning
OL,14,Findictment of the British State's use
OL,15,Fof its judicial system as a weapon of
OL,16,Fpolitical repression".
OL,18,F"Today, after 36 years, the truth has
OL,19,Fbeen officially acknowledged," the
OL,20,FNewry Sinn Fein councillor said.
