OL,7,F"This wasn't a miscarriage of justice
OL,8,F` it was the intended outcome of a
OL,9,Frigged system. I will not accept
OL,10,Ftoday's decision as closure, my case
OL,11,Fis just one example of hundreds.
OL,13,F"Today's ruling highlights again the
OL,14,Furgency and need for full
OL,15,Faccountability."
OL,17,FThe decision, by a two to one
OL,18,Fmajority, was based on an examination
OL,19,Fof a confidential section of documents.
