OL,5,Cfound
OL,7,FIn 1991 all three men were found
OL,8,Fguilty at a non-jury trial of
OL,9,Fpossessing explosive substances with
OL,10,Fintent.
OL,12,FThe charges related to a bomb planted
OL,13,Fat Limavady United FC's ground ahead
OL,14,Fof a home match against the RUC in
OL,15,FDecember 1989.
OL,17,FThe deadly device, made up of Semtex
OL,18,Fand ball bearings to act as shrapnel,
OL,19,Fhad been placed in the away dugout.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
