OL,3,CMen's 1991 convictions overturned
OL,4,Cafter 'deliberate police misconduct'
OL,5,Cfound
OL,7,FIt was to be detonated by radio remote
OL,8,Fcontrol when the police officers in
OL,9,Fthe RUC team were at that part of the
OL,10,Fstadium, previous courts heard.
OL,12,FThe terrorist plot was foiled due to
OL,13,Ffixture changes that meant the match
OL,14,Fdid not take place on the planned date.
OL,16,FThe statements given to the RMP were
OL,17,Fordered under compulsion, with no
OL,18,Fcaution given and with no opportunity
OL,19,Fto consult legal representatives.
