OL,3,CMen's 1991 convictions overturned
OL,4,Cafter 'deliberate police misconduct'
OL,5,Cfound
OL,7,FIt centred on the emergence of
OL,8,Fpotential fresh evidence which was not
OL,9,Fdisclosed at the original trial.
OL,11,FMost of the hearing took place in
OL,12,Fprivate due to the sensitivity of the
OL,13,Fmaterial.
OL,15,FSpecial advocates appointed to protect
OL,16,Fthe interests of the three appellants
OL,17,Fargued that if disclosure had been
OL,18,Fmade at trial it would have revealed
OL,19,Fserious misconduct by the police.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
