OL,4,Cafter 'deliberate police misconduct'
OL,5,Cfound
OL,7,FIn a brief, three-page judgment, they
OL,8,Fheld that the three men's appeals must
OL,9,Fbe allowed.
OL,11,FDissenting from their assessment, Lady
OL,12,FChief Justice Dame Siobhan Keegan
OL,13,Ffound on balance that the trial was
OL,14,Ffair and that the convictions remained
OL,15,Fsafe.
OL,17,F"While the conduct of the police is
OL,18,Freprehensible, this is outweighed by
OL,19,Fthe competing public interest in the
OL,20,Fprosecution of serious terrorist
OL,21,Foffences," she stated.
OL,26,@yD@AOU}D@JO]
