OL,5,Cfound
OL,7,FHowever, Dame Siobhan confirmed:
OL,8,F"Therefore, by a majority, the
OL,9,Fdecision of this court is that the
OL,10,Fconvictions are not safe on the abuse
OL,11,Fof process ground referred by the CCRC
OL,12,Fand argued by the Special Advocates."
OL,14,FSpeaking outside court, the three
OL,15,Fmen's solicitor declared them fully
OL,16,Fvindicated by the verdict.
OL,18,FGavin Booth of Phoenix Law said: "We
OL,19,Fwelcome the decision to quash the
OL,20,Fconvictions of Declan Murphy, Declan
OL,21,FMoen and Conor Gilmore.
