OL,7,F"Our clients' case always was that
OL,8,Fthey were set up by a state agent.
OL,10,F"That was endorsed today by the Court
OL,11,Fof Appeal openly stating that the
OL,12,Fconduct was reprehensible."
OL,14,FMr Booth added: "Today our clients are
OL,15,Ffinally vindicated after fighting this
OL,16,Fcase since 1989."
